@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative One

autonumber

actor "Collaborator" as Collaborator
participant ":System" as System

activate Collaborator

    Collaborator -> System : asks to show the list of tasks
    activate System

    System --> Collaborator : shows the list of tasks
    deactivate System

    Collaborator -> System : selects the task that wants to record the completion
    activate System

    System --> Collaborator : request confirmation
    deactivate System

    Collaborator -> System : confirms data
    activate System

    System --> Collaborator : display operation success
    deactivate System
@enduml